==製作==
電影的主要拍攝工作在[[瑞士|瑞士]]、[[亞塞拜然|亞塞拜然]]、[[法國|法國]]和[[巴西|巴西]]進行<ref>{{cite web|title=UNITED PASSIONS– FIRST EXCLUSIVE IMAGE|url=http://www.tf1international.com/tf1_news_article.php?Type=6&oId=17&PHPSESSID=78fef19ed722298c3d1ee305f73a1615|website=www.tf1international.com|accessdate=2014-06-21|archive-date=2014-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140511020351/http://www.tf1international.com/tf1_news_article.php?Type=6&oId=17&PHPSESSID=f65e5e27abb35116613fd42e2ee7a0d8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。FIFA希望電影在2014年夏天，即[[2014年世界盃|巴西世界盃]]舉行前完成<ref name="Ruth"/>。電影劇本只花了四個月便完成<ref name="Ruth"/>，FIFA最初建議電影名稱為「傳奇人物」（Men of Legend）或「締夢者」（Dreammakers）<ref name="Ikav">{{cite web|url=http://www.espnfc.com/fifa-world-cup/story/2496658/fifa-film-united-passions-among-worst-in-us-history|title=FIFA film 'United Passions' one of worst in U.S. box office history|author=ESPN Staff|work=''ESPN FC''|publisher=(ESPN)|date=2015-06-19|accessdate=2015-06-21|archive-date=2015-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621012944/http://www.espnfc.com/fifa-world-cup/story/2496658/fifa-film-united-passions-among-worst-in-us-history|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==上映==
此電影在美國上映日期與[[2015年國際足協收賄案|2015年國際足協收賄案]]事發時間相若，數名前FIFA執行委員會成員被捕及被控收賄<ref name="Scheck">{{cite news |last=Scheck |first=Frank |title='United Passions': Film Review |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/united-passions-film-review-799879 |newspaper=The Hollywood Reporter |accessdate=2015-06-04 |archive-date=2015-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150604184141/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/united-passions-film-review-799879 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此事導致主宰FIFA近17年的[[塞普·布拉特|塞普·布拉特]]辭職<ref>{{cite news |last=Parker |first=Graham |date=2015-06-02 |title=Sepp Blatter: A history of scandal |url=http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2015/6/2/sepp-blatter-a-history-of-scandal.html |publisher=Al Jazeera |access-date=2015-06-04 |archive-date=2015-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150604203159/http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2015/6/2/sepp-blatter-a-history-of-scandal.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影被指對FIFA存在已久的貪污問題視而不見，罗斯說他曾問製片商「那些貪腐劇情都去了哪？那些暗算、桌下交易的片段呢？」在電影上映前，喜劇演員[[约翰·奥利弗|约翰·奥利弗]]諷刺說道：「電影像FIFA一樣，很爛。」「哪有運動電影的英雄們都是行政人員<ref>{{YouTube |id=DlJEt2KU33I |title="Last Week Tonight with John Oliver: FIFA and the World Cup (HBO)"}}</ref>？」

== 反响 ==

===票房===
電影拍攝預算為2,500至3,200萬美元<ref name="FIFA"/>，而[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]的報導為約2,900萬美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-united-passions-review-20150605-story.html|title=FIFA-bankrolled 'United Passions' kicks far wide of its goal|author=Michael Rechtshaffen|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|publisher=(Tribune Publishing)|date=2015-06-04|accessdate=2015-06-08|archive-date=2015-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150608123052/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-united-passions-review-20150605-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大約1,700萬英鎊（約2,700萬美元，90%經費）費用由FIFA出資<ref name="Guardian">{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/oct/25/fifa-united-passions-pr-exercise-sepp-blatter|title=Fifa film United Passions is PR exercise that rankles even with its stars|author=James Riach|work=The Guardian|date=2014-10-25|accessdate=2015-06-08|archive-date=2015-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610050620/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/oct/25/fifa-united-passions-pr-exercise-sepp-blatter|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="FIFAFC">{{cite web|url=http://www.espnfc.com/international-friendly/story/2074836/fifa-film-united-passions-running-at-a-loss-of-$268-million|title=FIFA film United Passions 'running at a loss of $26.8 million'|author=Jeff Carlisle|work=ESPN FC|publisher=(ESPN)|date=2014-10-06|accessdate=2015-06-08|archive-date=2015-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610185248/http://www.espnfc.com/international-friendly/story/2074836/fifa-film-united-passions-running-at-a-loss-of-$268-million|dead-url=no}}</ref>，據報這部電影賠了2,680萬美元<ref name="FIFAFC"/>。

在北美地區，此片立即成為[[票房炸彈|票房炸彈]]<ref name="FIFA"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/sports/sportsnow/la-sp-sn-fifa-movie-united-passions-bombs-20150608-story.html|title='United Passions,' which cost FIFA $29 million, has $607 box-office take|author=Austin Knoblauch|work=Los Angeles Times|publisher=(Tribune Publishing)|date=2015-06-08|accessdate=2015-06-08|archive-date=2015-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150608205914/http://www.latimes.com/sports/sportsnow/la-sp-sn-fifa-movie-united-passions-bombs-20150608-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。於2015年6月5日上映，在美國上映的10家電影院中，首日票房收入只有319美元，第二天更跌至288美元<ref name="FIFA">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-fifa-movie-united-800664|title=Box Office: FIFA Movie 'United Passions' Bombs in U.S.|author=Pamela McClintock|work=The Hollywood Reporter|publisher=(Prometheus Global Media)|date=2015-06-07|accessdate=2015-06-08|archive-date=2015-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150608205541/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-fifa-movie-united-800664|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="3day">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-fifa-movie-united-801434|title=Box Office: FIFA Movie 'United Passions' Red-Carded in U.S. With $918 Debut|author=Pamela McClintock|work=The Hollywood Reporter|publisher=(Prometheus Global Media)|date=2015-06-09|accessdate=2015-06-10|archive-date=2015-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610053935/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-fifa-movie-united-801434|dead-url=no}}</ref>。上映首三天的收入只有918美元，成為美國有史以來上映票房最差的電影<ref name="3day"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.hollywoodreporter.com/entry/view/id/969041|title=Box-Office Bombs: 6 of the Lowest U.S. Openings of All Time|author=Pamela McClintock|work=''The Hollywood Reporter''|publisher=(Prometheus Global Media)|date=2015-06-17|accessdate=2015-06-17}}</ref>，[[鳳凰城市中心|鳳凰城市中心]]的一家電影院更只有9美元收入，表示只有一名觀眾入場<ref name="FIFA"/>。票房慘淡，使發行商在周末過後把該電影下片。聯合激情打破了2012年電影《[[我吻了一个吸血鬼|我吻了一个吸血鬼]]》的紀錄，成為北美史上票房最差的電影<ref name="App">{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/jun/18/fifas-united-passions-lowest-grossing-film-us-history|title=Fifa's United Passions confirmed as lowest-grossing film in US history|author=Ben Child|work=The Guardian|publisher=(Guardian Media Group)|date=2015-06-18|accessdate=2015-06-20|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619175359/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/jun/18/fifas-united-passions-lowest-grossing-film-us-history|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Ikav"/>。

《聯合激情》曾在2014年10月5日在[[蘇黎世電影節|蘇黎世電影節]]的一個500座劇院放映，約120人購買22.7美元的票入場觀看<ref name="FIFAFC"/><ref name="Independent">{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/news-and-comment/fifa-film-united-passions-cost-19m-so-far-it-has-made-125000-at-the-box-office-9779704.html|title=Fifa film United Passions cost £19m, so far it has made £125,000 at the box office|author=Simon Rice|work=The Independent|date=2014-10-06|accessdate=2015-06-08|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626070130/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/news-and-comment/fifa-film-united-passions-cost-19m-so-far-it-has-made-125000-at-the-box-office-9779704.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除了北美地區，此電影收入最高的地區是[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]及[[獨立國家聯合體|獨聯體]]（£144,000）、[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]（£4,000）和塞爾維亞（£2,000），在[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]、[[斯洛文尼亞|斯洛文尼亞]]、[[瑞士|瑞士]]和[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]的票房收入少得可憐<ref name="FIFAFC"/><ref name="Independent"/>，法國更乾脆直接發行[[DVD|DVD]]<ref name="Guardian"/>。

導演弗里德里克·奥伯汀在美國票房很慘後首次接受訪問時，向[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]說他嘗試在[[华特迪士尼公司|迪士尼]]宣傳片和[[科斯塔·加夫拉斯|科斯塔·加夫拉斯]]／[[麥可·摩爾|麥可·摩爾]]式電影中取得平衡，但電影最終只能迎合FIFA的喜好。「現在我的名字跟把[[愛滋病|愛滋病]]傳入非洲和造成經濟危機的人一樣臭名遠播<ref name="Ruth">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/fifa-movie-director-breaks-silence-802760|title=FIFA Movie Director Breaks Silence on Bomb: "It's a Disaster; My Name Is All Over [This Mess]"|author=Scott Roxborough and Rhonda Richford|work=''The Hollywood Reporter''|publisher=(Prometheus Global Media)|date=2015-06-17|accessdate=2015-06-17|archive-date=2015-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617192348/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/fifa-movie-director-breaks-silence-802760|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」主演蒂姆·罗斯不斷地被媒體要求對該電影發言，在2015年5月FIFA貪污事件曝光前向《[[世界報_(德國)|世界報]]》自爆並沒有看過電影：「我抱歉當時沒有質問導演和劇本。」他自認看錢份上而拍攝，片酬能填補他的財政缺口，說道：「你知道嗎？FIFA自挖的財政洞口已深不見底<ref name="Ruth"/>。」

=== 评价 ===
《聯合激情》上映后遭遇压倒性的负面评价。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]上收集的13篇专业评论文章中没有任何一篇给予“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”低至0%（最高100%）<ref>{{Rotten Tomatoes|id=united_passions|title=United Passions}}</ref>。而从[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]收集的7篇評論看中，影片的平均得分仅为1（满分100）<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/united-passions | title=United Passions | work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] | accessdate=2015-06-05 | archive-date=2018-06-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180626143927/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/united-passions | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

電影被指劇情差劣<ref name="Hoffman">{{cite news |last=Hoffman |first=Jordan |author-link= |title=United Passions review – Fifa propaganda is pure cinematic excrement |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/jun/04/united-passions-review-tim-roth-sam-neill-gerard-depardieu |newspaper=The Guardian |access-date=2015-06-04 |archive-date=2015-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150604171401/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/jun/04/united-passions-review-tim-roth-sam-neill-gerard-depardieu |dead-url=no }}</ref>、名稱不合<ref>{{cite news |last=Berry |first=Dan |date=2015-06-02 |title=FIFA Film: An Epic Fantasy |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/06/02/sports/fifa-film-an-epic-fantasy.html |newspaper=The New York Times |access-date=2015-06-04 |archive-date=2015-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150603051241/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/06/02/sports/fifa-film-an-epic-fantasy.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>以及帶有偏見，《[[衛報|衛報]]》影評員評此電影為「電影糞便」和「自我陶醉」<ref name="Hoffman" />，其它人的評語亦包括「阿諛奉承，自吹自擂」<ref name="Scheck" />、「超級愚蠢」
